Experiment 13: 
Write a shell script to find the sum of the first n natural numbers using a for loop.

naturalno.sh
#!/bin/bash
read -p "Enter n: " n
sum=0
for (( i=1; i<=n; i++ ))
do
    sum=$((sum + i))
done
echo "Sum of first $n natural numbers is $sum"

